summary: CUSTOM PIKACHU-THEMED AIR JORDANS SPOTTED ON THE DETECTIVE PIKACHU "YELLOW CARPET"
title: CUSTOM PIKACHU-THEMED AIR JORDANS SPOTTED ON THE DETECTIVE PIKACHU "YELLOW CARPET"
body: Detective Pikachu’s premiere in Hollywood rolled out the yellow carpet for the star-studded action. Among those who hit the event were Kong: Skull Island director Jordan Vogt-Roberts, who just happened to be wearing a pair of custom Pikachu-themed AJ1s. I can’t tell if I love or hate them, but they’re certainly unique!
